text: that’s fair. THank you <@UGY22E2KC> Do you know if we’ll still have access to the analytics if I archive them?

Yes, you’ll still be able to see the analytics from the Details page. Note that if you _also_ Unpublish the page, you’ll need to click on the More button >> Details, rather than just clicking on the name of the page (clicking the name of an unpublished page, archived or not, will always bring you to the editor).
